Stratum Privacy Policy
VS Code Plugin — Stratum IDE by Stratum Inc.
Effective Date: 14.03.2026    |   Last Updated: 14.03.2026   |   Version 1.0

Plain-English Summary
Stratum reads your source files and project models to power its canvases — this data stays on your machine and is never sent to Stratum's servers. The only data that ever leaves your machine is (a) your description text when you use the NL input feature, and only after you explicitly consent, and (b) anonymous usage counts if you opt in. We do not sell your data. We do not mine your code. We do not build profiles of you.

